{
  "texts": [
    "Duplication check: Duplicated papers were identified and removed.",
    "Given the extensiveness of Google Scholar's database, there were instances where the same paper was indexed multiple times. iii.",
    "Full text review: For papers that passed the initial screening, a full review of the text body was conducted to assess their suitability.",
    "Only papers that had fully accessible text and were directly relevant to the research topic were retained. iv.",
    "Relevance and quality check: Papers that did not provide substantive insights or lacked rigorous methodology, even if they touched upon the research topic, were also excluded to ensure the quality of the final sample."
  ]
}